{"type":null,"faqId":49981,"title":"华为智能手表_拿到手表后，如何开始使用？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body28311181\"><ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__ol16420978\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li53474037\">拿到手表后，请您使用手机扫描手表屏幕二维码，或在华为应用市场搜索 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__b4669345316235\">Android Wear 中国版 </strong>下载并安装 Android Wear&#8482; 中国版app。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li44385268162324\">手表开机，向左滑动屏幕至二维码界面。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li64038986162336\">打开 Android Wear&#8482; 中国版app，跟随app的屏幕提示通过蓝牙连接完成手机和手表的配对、同步。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li65124744\">配对、同步成功后，手表的时间和各项信息已经初始化，您就可以正常使用手表了。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li49251786\">同步完成后请跟随手表的屏幕提示滑动手指，学习常用手势和基本操作。</li></ol><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__note13571075\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4df_h6x3n.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__ul40612898\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li29971768\">请勿直接使用手机的蓝牙功能配对手表，需要在Android Wear 中国版app中完成配对操作。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329143__li1310461\">如果配对失败，手表无法正常使用。</li></ul></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":497,"faqType":"产品介绍","useful":6,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329143","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Introduction","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627735000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":382,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"开始，使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}